{"tid":829972,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[續]之前公司新黎90 後為煙Break而食煙之後居然 .... 搞到我好尷尬!","createTime":"2018-09-21T00:33:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T02:50:56.000Z","uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"38bd957f445f8c3eb81a0b1c98aee550f70b453e","tid":829972,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T00:33:09.000Z","msg":"之前個90 後見帶水樽唔食煙埋唔到<br />\n終於明白團結就是力量, 開始食煙<br />\n雖然只係薄荷煙, 好撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日做野辛苦, 又要social下同同事聯絡感情, 我地呢行人際關係好緊要 , 就迫住3 點落樓下食下煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母食完煙個個都飛個煙頭落地嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n個90 後開頭都手持住個煙頭返公司門口個垃圾筒dom ....比我地笑佢[呀仔你搞乜呀] <br />\n見到佢食唔慣又迫住食真係嘰一聲笑左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知今個星期戲肉就黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個新黎90後居然拎住個易極盒裝煙頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有Sen 少少80 後同事細細聲問我條靚係咪儲開煙頭 ... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2795b4110bd66200dae6bbba126e94159c9efb","tid":829972,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T00:40:44.000Z","msg":"🚬🐋💬"},{"pid":"cfb4ead97e0d3d417ef55ff0d402c8cbce0052c4","tid":829972,"uid":196708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T00:46:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ae489deb89af673e825ca6e20796db33d10ff36","tid":829972,"uid":29880,"like"